RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.SqlString: SELECT VqVideoStreamResults.DstAddr AS 'Destination Address', VqVideoStreamResults.DstUdpPort AS 'Destination UDP Port', VqVideoStreamResults.RtpTransportPktCount AS 'Received RTP Transport Packets', VqVideoStreamResults.RtpPktLostCount AS 'Lost RTP Transport Packets', VqVideoStreamResults.RtpPktDiscardedCount AS 'Discarded RTP Transport Packets', VqVideoStreamResults.RtpPktOosCount AS 'Out-of-sequence RTP Transport Packets', VqVideoStreamResults.RtpPktDuplicateCount AS 'Duplicate RTP Transport Packets', VqVideoStreamResults.RtpTimestampErrorCount AS 'RTP Transport Timestamp Errors' FROM VqVideoStreamResults, VqProbeChannelBlock WHERE ( VqVideoStreamResults.ParentHnd = VqProbeChannelBlock.Handle AND VqVideoStreamResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND VqProbeChannelBlock.DataSetId = @DataSetId ) UNION SELECT VqVideoStreamResults.DstAddr AS 'Destination Address', VqVideoStreamResults.DstUdpPort AS 'Destination UDP Port', VqVideoStreamResults.RtpTransportPktCount AS 'Received RTP Transport Packets', VqVideoStreamResults.RtpPktLostCount AS 'Lost RTP Transport Packets', VqVideoStreamResults.RtpPktDiscardedCount AS 'Discarded RTP Transport Packets', VqVideoStreamResults.RtpPktOosCount AS 'Out-of-sequence RTP Transport Packets', VqVideoStreamResults.RtpPktDuplicateCount AS 'Duplicate RTP Transport Packets', VqVideoStreamResults.RtpTimestampErrorCount AS 'RTP Transport Timestamp Errors' FROM VqVideoStreamResults, VqDeviceChannelBlock WHERE ( VqVideoStreamResults.ParentHnd = VqDeviceChannelBlock.Handle AND VqVideoStreamResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND VqDeviceChannelBlock.DataSetId = @DataSetId )
